relation: Upgraded for iOS 6.0, now using Automatic Reference Counting (ARC), updated to adopt current best practices for Objective-C.
Upgraded project to build with the iOS 4.0 SDK.
Improve the accessibility of AccelerometerGraph through use of the iPhone Accessibility API.
Updated to implement significant architecture and performance improvements. Added a low-pass filter and adaptive filtering options.
